OL,3,CMaternity services at Daisy Hill
OL,4,CHospital resume
OL,6,FMaternity services at Daisy Hill
OL,7,FHospital have resumed following a
OL,8,Ftemporary suspension due to staff
OL,9,Fshortages.
OL,11,FEarlier, the Southern Health and
OL,12,FSocial Care Trust said due to
OL,13,F"unexpected staff sickness" within
OL,14,Fobstetrics and gynaecology services,
OL,15,Fthey would be "unable to provide safe
OL,16,Fmedical cover" at the Newry site.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/4
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,416,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1782134325
OL,3,CMaternity services at Daisy Hill
OL,4,CHospital resume
OL,6,FHowever, in an update the trust said
OL,7,F"business as usual" would resume at
OL,8,FDaisy Hill from 9pm on Saturday after
OL,9,Fmedical cover was "successfully
OL,10,Fsecured".
OL,12,FDiversions to Craigavon Area Hospital
OL,13,Fhad been in place.
OL,15,FThe trust apologised for "any worry or
OL,16,Finconvenience" caused.
OL,18,FThe trust said they continue to "face
OL,19,Fongoing medical staffing challenges"
OL,20,Fwithin obstetrics and gynaecology at
OL,21,FDaisy Hill Hospital.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/4
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
