OL,3,CMaternity services at Daisy Hill
OL,4,CHospital resume
OL,6,FThey said: "Whilst we always work hard
OL,7,Fto avoid this, this divert was part of
OL,8,Four established service continuity
OL,9,Farrangements, which are designed by
OL,10,Four clinical teams to maintain safe,
OL,11,Fhigh-quality care when staffing
OL,12,Fpressures arise."
OL,14,FInitially, they said the decision was
OL,15,Ftaken to "ensure the safety of women
OL,16,Fand babies".
OL,18,FCatch up with the latest UTV Live on
